# Common Interview Questions

## Q1. What is incremental loading?

Loading only new or changed records instead of full dataset reload.

---

## Q2. Why incremental loading important?

Improves performance and reduces cost.

---

## Q3. Difference between CDC and incremental load?

CDC detects changes; incremental loading processes those changes.

---

## Q4. What is watermark?

Checkpoint storing latest processed record/time.

---

## Q5. What is upsert?

Update existing row or insert new row.

